text: Jules Winslow Wright (August 21, 1933 â€“ January 11, 2022) was an American businessman and politician. He was born in Nenana, Alaska. Wright died on January 11, 2022 in Wasilla, Alaska at the age of 88. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2022 deaths Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from Alaska Category:Businesspeople from Alaska Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
